## Your task

Using the scores and evidence above, generate ONLY the narrative sections listed below. Do NOT recompute or override any scores. Return ONLY JSON.

```json
{
  "overall_summary": "Two-sentence summary of overall performance.",
  "car_analysis": {
    "context": {"status": "Strong/Partial/Weak", "feedback": "One-line feedback"},
    "action":  {"status": "Strong/Partial/Weak", "feedback": "One-line feedback"},
    "result":  {"status": "Strong/Partial/Weak", "feedback": "One-line feedback"}
  },
  "car_insight": "One-sentence overall CAR observation.",
  "strengths": [
